- A rogue assassin vs. a literal mountain. A warrior of sunlight vs. a mermaid. A treasure hunter vs. a blind monk. Experience innovative gameplay across wholly unique champions.
- Familiar favorites like Akali, Seraphine, Jinx, Caitlyn, Vi, Jayce, and more champions from the League of Legends PC title, faithfully adapted to play great on mobile!
- Whatever you want your legend to be, there’s a champ waiting for you.

PREMIUM MOBILE MOBA EXPERIENCE
- Stunning visuals, beautiful graphics, and vibrant characters.
- Multiplayer game modes, champions, and skins are constantly updated.
- The 5v5 battles of League of Legends, optimized for an epic mobile experience.
- Ever-changing, high-quality content.

FREE TO PLAY, ALWAYS FAIR
- Skill level and party size are a priority in matchmaking balance for each mobile battle.
- Earn all champions for free in Wild Rift just by playing! There will never be exclusively purchasable champions.
- No intrusive ads. No paying for power. No paying for play time. Ever.

Go for the big plays in the ultimate battle arena competition. Experience the action-packed gameplay Riot Games is known for with League of Legends: Wild Rift.
